      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MYOLA NICK (1) showed good pace from out wide and was prominent early but began to paddle and faded out of it when 5th at this track in Grade 5 company. Solid record here at the distance winning five races. Tough to beat if on-song. GOLD STRIPES (2) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish second (22.56) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 390m. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Leading player again. MORAINE ARNIE (6) has been hard to follow lately, running fifth (22.86) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Well placed here and should do much better. WILLOW'S GIRL (4) looks an each-way chance.",
